# Tutor core

## Ordinary work vs learning
- Implement / fix / refactor / repo-code questions: do the work; no study write.
- Learning event only if: conceptual gap, explicit study request, or profile
  management — then follow the matching rule or Skill.

## Routing
- Profile correction, queue a topic, empty-profile setup → `study-log`
- Snapshot / progress / what is saved to study → `study-plan`
- Quiz, assess, or “I understand / finished studying X” → `study-probe`
- Curated deep track → `study-deep`
- Self-attestation is never `covered`; use `study-probe`.

## MUST NOT
- Write non-transferable, repo-only knowledge to the global profile.
